item.title: Melissa + Darnell SDE (Same Day Edit)
item.description:
Melissa + Darnell SDE (Same Day Edit)

It was a whole lot of wedding packed into a very short amount of time! Normally on a SDE, the ceremony is at least a few hours before the reception... but not this day! Ceremony ended at 5pm, Reception started at 7pm and the last event in the video was at 9pm.

item.title: Tami + Scott
item.description:
Tami + Scott

Much like I meet my own wife, these Tami and Scoot met overseas and made a long distance romance into a full-time relationship. Tami and Scott are sure to have many more adventures in life... and from what I heard at the reception, they will have plenty of family and friends rooting them on!

item.title: Lynette + Hector Extended-Cut
item.description:
Lynette + Hector Extended-Cut

This was one of the nicest families we have ever shot. Rene and I felt like one of the family members and had a great time watching the events unfold. This group was ready to party, once the events were finished... and if we did not have a long drive home, we might have stayed!

item.title: Yana + David
item.description:
Yana + David

What a classy event at the Mt. Woodson Castle. Charming with a nice old world feel. It was good that Yana and David decided to get married in late summer with plenty of sunshine. At some point the power went out and it took some time for the problem to be fixed...

item.title: Carly + Nick
item.description:
Carly + Nick

What a party! The band was ripping it at the Fairbanks Ranch Country Club! Carly and Nick were having so much fun dancing that they did not even want to stop the party for and old fashioned bouquet toss or cake cutting. They did do the parent dances and let a few people say some nice things...
